---
title: Seared Beef & Caramelised Onion Ciabatta with Fries & Creamy Pesto
description: When making an open-faced ciabatta sandwich you want to have the best flavour combos in town. Beef strips, caramelised onion and a creamy pesto dressing have to be the winner because we can’t get enough of them!

